{"tid":2030117,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《表姐》30年前預言若幹部不滿即「一國兩制」完了！","createTime":"2020-05-22T14:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T15:16:46.000Z","uid":44730,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dae0f7b4671e828ae69d183ab1962f542c14ccde","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/zcVN3vKG54JJpVnuBz2ODrv2TjA=/412x231/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3QJZP7BXPGFTBIFL2ZQFYHHMK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FzcVN3vKG54JJpVnuBz2ODrv2TjA%3D%2F412x231%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3QJZP7BXPGFTBIFL2ZQFYHHMK4.jpg&h=72a14449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大公佈「港版國安法」提案，香港將被推向自治全失。中共今次繞過立法會直接訂立「港版國安法」，令《基本法》名存實亡。一國兩制隨時變相成「一國一制」，網民即瘋傳Do姐神預言「一國兩制玩完後，香港股市會跌跌跌」&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"d08a3a59cd85a70de4e9db94086cd609472230f8","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"不少網民瘋傳1990年由張堅庭執導、鄭裕玲（Do姐）主演電影《表姐，妳好嘢！》的片段，兼重溫曾被中共以造成「人民內部矛盾」為由，被例入黑名單的《表姐》系列。<br />\n<br />\n導演張堅庭曾在1989年六四上北京支持民運人士，去年6月亦有參與反修例大遊行，當時他已提到若惡法通過，香港只會繼續變差。今年3月，張堅庭接受港台節目訪問時又講到，若23條惡法通過，自己極有可能因拍過四集電影《表姐，妳好嘢！》而被追究。"},{"pid":"74c79089624dcfec36888f414d85816027b37e5c","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"的確，今日在網上瘋傳的兩段《表姐》影片中，第一集當飾演大陸女公安幹部鄭大姐的Do姐被方剛捉走後，Do姐就搬出隸屬27軍的爸爸來嚇方剛及其黨羽，表示若他不高興的話，就會命令弟子兵來港：「嘿！到時聯合聲明，完喇！一國兩制，完喇！基本法，完喇！到時港幣大跌，金融大跌，股市大跌，樓價大跌，跌跌跌跌跌！」而股市大跌，正正就是今日香港所經歷的事情。<br />\n<br />\n另外一條，則是《表姐》第3集，Do姐跟飾演政治部督察呂sir的黃秋生提到，就算做過對黨及國家不利的事情，只要有悔意仍會有飯食：「只要冇講一啲對黨同國家不利嘅說話，冇諗過一啲危害黨同國家嘅嘢，冇做過一啲與黨為敵嘅事情，或者冇睇過一啲醜化黨同國家嘅電影，冇參加過皇后大道東示威遊行嘅人呢，大把前途嘅。但若然你有做過而有悔意嘅呢，都可以申請公屋㗎喎。但係你做咗，冇悔意，堅持嘅呢，咁難搞喇。咁我哋先至會唔畀飯佢食，同剝奪佢人權嘅啫。」"},{"pid":"0319ba0e74472dadf051183850a798f9a0b625c9","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/JXjeq-tXKfbBbD3b_GCgiZI_2GE=/412x257/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XSZKFTRRTNEWPLGF2CTYMD2WUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FJXjeq-tXKfbBbD3b_GCgiZI_2GE%3D%2F412x257%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXSZKFTRRTNEWPLGF2CTYMD2WUU.jpg&h=2cd4ee15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91b127eff9e33b336f1554f24d4f06332aea6488","tid":2030117,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"[文長慎入]中共已經｢哂冷｣，香港人選擇下注還是下跪？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029861</a>"},{"pid":"6108034fb49d676233edebaf0d3c8501c1610944","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8rvLzMBRExw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8rvLzMBRExw&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CEtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=555754ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8rvLzMBRExw</a><br />\n<br />\n諗起笑聲救地球 97前後 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef82b6fc1a068f72f4a7fb1088e7ee0207e304ea","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6108034fb49d676233edebaf0d3c8501c1610944","tid":2030117,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8rvLzMBRExw\" data-sr-url